code: public Map execute(Exchange exchange, Object rowData) {     Map<String, Object> params = new HashMap<>().     for (InParameter inParameter : inParameterList) {         params.put(inParameter.getName(), inParameter.getValueExtractor().eval(exchange, rowData)).     }     for (InOutParameter inOutParameter : inOutParameterList) {         params.put(inOutParameter.getOutValueMapKey(), inOutParameter.getValueExtractor().eval(exchange, rowData)).     }     LOG.debug("Invoking stored procedure: {}", template.getProcedureName()).     return super.execute(params). }
